I have got the idea from this page iwongsakorn.com/tag/kana-scalper/
 and wrote my own kana scalper. This strategy draws 3 200 ATR level along side with the sma. It uses 200 ema as trend. Once the price approaches the 20 ema. it will place orders according to trend and take profit and stop loss quickly using the 200 ATR lines.

This is a quick scalper strategy with winrate over 50%
